attachments.title: The Extremely Cursed Boat Flip Turd Guy Explains Himself
attachments.text: It’s not everyday you see a guy doing a shit flip into water Welcome to a special emergency Hell World. Please consider subscribing to support important work like this. Mention the city of Liverpool, England and a few iconic cultural touchstones likely come to mind. It’s the birthplace of the Beatles of course, not to mention other musical favorites like Echo and the Bunnymen and Ladytron to name a few. It’s got a proud literary and artistic tradition, and boasts of two widely popular football clubs. After he visited in the sixties Allen Ginsberg once famously called it "the center of consciousness of the human universe."
